project_descr: PAL/ Construction of Demolished Homes for NON REFUGEE Families in Gaza Strip

outputs.output_descr: - 200 rehousing units for non-refugee families will be constructed, around 75,000 workdays will be generated and approximately 11,000 square meter of roads will be tiled, 1,100 meter of water pipes will be installed, 1,100 meter of sewage pipes will be installed and an electrical network will be installed. Due to limitation of budget and prolonged implementation due to political resons, the number of housing units was reduced to 120 after the consent of the donor.

project_title: pal/ construction of demolished homes for non refugee
